      <title>简洁的架构</title>
      <link href="/2024/06/13/%E7%AE%80%E6%B4%81%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84/"/>
      <url>/2024/06/13/%E7%AE%80%E6%B4%81%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<pre class="mermaid">graph LR    A[Frameworks & Drivers] --> B[Interface Adapters]    B --> C[Use Cases]    C --> D[Entities]    classDef f fill:#e0f2fe,stroke:#0369a1;    classDef a fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a;    classDef u fill:#fef9c3,stroke:#ca8a04;    classDef e fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#dc2626;    class A f    class B a    class C u    class D e</pre><p>Clean Architecture(Robert C. Martin) 的核心思想是通过分层和依赖规则，实现软件系统的高内聚、低耦合，从而提升可维护性、可测试性和可扩展性。其关键在于将业务逻辑与外部技术细节（如数据库、框架、UI、Web 服务等）彻底分离，确保系统的核心——也就是业务规则——不依赖于任何外部组件。</p><p>这一架构强调“依赖倒置原则”：高层模块（如用例、业务逻辑）不应依赖低层模块（如数据库、网络），两者都应依赖于抽象。所有依赖关系必须指向系统内部，即从外层（技术细节层）向内层（业务核心层）流动，而内层对最外层一无所知。</p><p>Clean Architecture 通常将系统划分为多个同心圆层，从内到外依次是：Entities（实体，代表核心业务对象和规则）、Use Cases（用例，封装具体业务逻辑）、Interface Adapters（接口适配器，如控制器、数据转换器，用于连接内外）、Frameworks and Drivers（框架与驱动，包括数据库、Web 框架、UI 等）。越靠近中心，越稳定、越通用；越靠外层，越易变、越具体。</p><p>通过这种结构，业务逻辑可以独立于技术栈进行开发和测试，即使更换数据库、UI 框架或部署方式，也不会影响核心业务规则，从而显著提升系统的长期可维护性和适应变化的能力。</p><h2 id="它到底想解决什么？"><a href="#它到底想解决什么？" class="headerlink" title="它到底想解决什么？"></a>它到底想解决什么？</h2><p>想象一下：你写了一个用户注册功能，直接在 Flask 路由里连数据库、校验邮箱、插入数据——代码跑得挺快，但很快问题来了：</p><ul><li>想换数据库？得改业务逻辑。</li><li>想写单元测试？得先起个数据库。</li><li>想加个命令行入口？得把 Web 逻辑拆出来。</li><li>业务规则一变，整个文件都得动。</li></ul><p>Clean Architecture 的核心思路很简单：<strong>把“业务逻辑”和“技术细节”分开，让前者不依赖后者</strong>。</p><p>怎么分？靠两件事：</p><ol><li><strong>分层</strong>：把代码按职责分成几层，越往里越“纯粹”，只关心业务；越往外越“具体”，处理数据库、HTTP、文件等。</li><li><strong>依赖方向</strong>：内层不知道外层的存在，外层去实现内层定义的接口。</li></ol><p>这样一来，换数据库、加 API、写测试，都只动外层，核心逻辑几乎不用改。</p><h2 id="一个具体的例子：用户注册"><a href="#一个具体的例子：用户注册" class="headerlink" title="一个具体的例子：用户注册"></a>一个具体的例子：用户注册</h2><pre class="mermaid">%%{init: {'theme': 'base', 'themeVariables': { 'fontSize': '14px'}} }%%flowchart LR    classDef framework fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#3b82f6,color:#1e40af;    classDef adapter fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#22c55e,color:#166534;    classDef usecase fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#f59e0b,color:#92400e;    classDef entity fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#ef4444,color:#b91c1c;    subgraph Frameworks["Frameworks & Drivers"]        F1["📄 main.py"]        F2["🗃️ SQLite"]    end    subgraph Adapters["Interface Adapters\n(适配器)"]        A1["🔄 SqliteUserRepository"]        A2["🔄 InMemoryUserRepository"]    end    subgraph UseCases["Use Cases\n(业务用例)"]        U1["🧩 RegisterUser"]    end    subgraph Entities["Entities\n(核心业务)"]        E1["📝 UserRepository (接口)"]        E2["👤 User (实体)"]    end    %% 依赖关系：全部从外向内（左 → 右）    F1 --> A1    F2 --> A1    A1 --> U1    A2 --> U1    U1 --> E1    E1 --> E2    class F1,F2 framework    class A1,A2 adapter    class U1 usecase    class E1,E2 entity</pre><p>我们用一个极简的用户注册功能来演示。项目结构如下：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">user_service/</span><br><span class="line">├── main.py</span><br><span class="line">├── entities/</span><br><span class="line">│   └── user_repository.py</span><br><span class="line">├── use_cases/</span><br><span class="line">│   └── register_user.py</span><br><span class="line">├── adapters/</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── sqlite_user_repository.py</span><br><span class="line">│   └── in_memory_user_repository.py</span><br><span class="line">└── tests/</span><br><span class="line">    └── test_register_user.py</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="第一步：定义“我需要什么”（内核）"><a href="#第一步：定义“我需要什么”（内核）" class="headerlink" title="第一步：定义“我需要什么”（内核）"></a>第一步：定义“我需要什么”（内核）</h3><p>业务逻辑说：“我需要一个能存用户的地方。”<br>但它不关心是存到 SQLite、PostgreSQL，还是内存里。所以，我们先定义一个接口：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># entities/user_repository.py</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">UserRepository</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">save</span>(<span class="params">self, name: <span class="built_in">str</span>, email: <span class="built_in">str</span></span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">raise</span> NotImplementedError</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后写注册逻辑，只依赖这个接口：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># use_cases/register_user.py</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> entities.user_repository <span class="keyword">import</span> UserRepository</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">RegisterUser</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="params">self, user_repo: UserRepository</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.user_repo = user_repo</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">execute</span>(<span class="params">self, name: <span class="built_in">str</span>, email: <span class="built_in">str</span></span>) -&gt; <span class="built_in">str</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="string">&quot;@&quot;</span> <span class="keyword">not</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> email:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">raise</span> ValueError(<span class="string">&quot;邮箱格式错误&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.user_repo.save(name, email)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">&quot;注册成功！&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注意：这段代码里没有任何 <code>import sqlite3</code>、<code>import flask</code>，也没有任何具体技术。它只做一件事：<strong>描述业务规则</strong>。</p><h3 id="第二步：实现“怎么存”（外层）"><a href="#第二步：实现“怎么存”（外层）" class="headerlink" title="第二步：实现“怎么存”（外层）"></a>第二步：实现“怎么存”（外层）</h3><p>现在，我们提供两种实现：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># adapters/sqlite_user_repository.py</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> sqlite3</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> entities.user_repository <span class="keyword">import</span> UserRepository</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">SqliteUserRepository</span>(<span class="title class_ inherited__">UserRepository</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">save</span>(<span class="params">self, name: <span class="built_in">str</span>, email: <span class="built_in">str</span></span>):</span><br><span class="line">        conn = sqlite3.connect(<span class="string">&quot;users.db&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        conn.execute(<span class="string">&quot;INSERT INTO users (name, email) VALUES (?, ?)&quot;</span>, (name, email))</span><br><span class="line">        conn.commit()</span><br><span class="line">        conn.close()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># adapters/in_memory_user_repository.py</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> entities.user_repository <span class="keyword">import</span> UserRepository</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">InMemoryUserRepository</span>(<span class="title class_ inherited__">UserRepository</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.users = []</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">save</span>(<span class="params">self, name: <span class="built_in">str</span>, email: <span class="built_in">str</span></span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.users.append(&#123;<span class="string">&quot;name&quot;</span>: name, <span class="string">&quot;email&quot;</span>: email&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这两个类都实现了同一个接口，但一个写数据库，一个只存内存。业务逻辑完全不用知道区别。</p><h3 id="第三步：对象装配"><a href="#第三步：对象装配" class="headerlink" title="第三步：对象装配"></a>第三步：对象装配</h3><p>在程序入口，我们决定用哪个实现：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># main.py</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> use_cases.register_user <span class="keyword">import</span> RegisterUser</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> adapters.sqlite_user_repository <span class="keyword">import</span> SqliteUserRepository</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="string">&quot;__main__&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    repo = SqliteUserRepository()</span><br><span class="line">    use_case = RegisterUser(repo)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(use_case.execute(<span class="string">&quot;小明&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;xiaoming@example.com&quot;</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果哪天想换数据库，只需要改这一行：<code>repo = PostgresUserRepository()</code>，其他地方不动。</p><h3 id="第四步：测试变得很简单"><a href="#第四步：测试变得很简单" class="headerlink" title="第四步：测试变得很简单"></a>第四步：测试变得很简单</h3><p>因为业务逻辑不依赖数据库，测试可以直接用内存实现：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># tests/test_register_user.py</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> use_cases.register_user <span class="keyword">import</span> RegisterUser</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> adapters.in_memory_user_repository <span class="keyword">import</span> InMemoryUserRepository</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">test_invalid_email</span>():</span><br><span class="line">    repo = InMemoryUserRepository()</span><br><span class="line">    use_case = RegisterUser(repo)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">try</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        use_case.execute(<span class="string">&quot;小明&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;bad-email&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">assert</span> <span class="literal">False</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">except</span> ValueError:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">pass</span>  <span class="comment"># 预期行为</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>不需要 mock 数据库连接，也不用清理测试数据，跑得快，结果稳。</p><h2 id="依赖关系长什么样？"><a href="#依赖关系长什么样？" class="headerlink" title="依赖关系长什么样？"></a>依赖关系长什么样？</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">main.py</span><br><span class="line">   │</span><br><span class="line">   ▼</span><br><span class="line">use_cases/ ────依赖───▶ entities/</span><br><span class="line">   ▲                    ▲</span><br><span class="line">   │                    │</span><br><span class="line">adapters/ ───实现───────┘</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><code>use_cases</code> 只知道 <code>entities</code> 里的接口；</li><li><code>adapters</code> 实现这些接口；</li><li><code>main.py</code> 负责把它们“拼”在一起；</li><li><strong>内层代码从不 import 外层</strong>。</li></ul><p>这就是所谓的“依赖向内”——不是规定，而是为了隔离变化。</p><h2 id="小结"><a href="#小结" class="headerlink" title="小结"></a>小结</h2><p>一开始觉得这种结构“太重”，一个小功能搞这么多文件。但后来发现：</p><ul><li>当项目变大，改需求、加功能时，<strong>知道哪些代码能动、哪些不能动，比什么都重要</strong>；</li><li>测试写起来轻松很多，尤其是回归测试；</li><li>团队协作时，有人改数据库、有人写 API，只要接口不变，互不干扰。</li></ul><p>当然，<strong>不是所有项目都需要这么分</strong>。如果你写个一次性脚本，直接写也没问题。但当你希望代码“活得久一点”，这种分离会带来长期收益。</p><p>Clean Architecture 不是银弹，也不是必须遵守的教条。<br>它只是提供了一种思路：<strong>让业务逻辑独立于技术细节</strong>。<br>目录结构、分层命名，都是为了服务于这个目标。</p><p>可以从一个小功能开始尝试——比如把数据库操作抽成一个接口，业务逻辑只依赖它。<br>不用一步到位，慢慢体会它带来的好处就好。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
